5. Build Philosophy
- Build in phases.
- Validate the core learning loop before adding advanced features.
- Keep the architecture modular.
- Prefer clarity over complexity.
- Keep the product focused on exam preparation and retention.

6. Core Development Sequence
1. Business and product clarity.
2. Database and API foundation.
3. Flutter app MVP.
4. Admin panel MVP.
5. Community features.
6. Analytics layer.
7. AI assistance.
8. AI tutor.

